Ilmify (‚Äúwe‚Äù, ‚Äúour‚Äù, ‚Äúus‚Äù) respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how information is collected, used, stored, and shared when you use the Ilmify mobile application.

1. About the App

Ilmify is a platform that connects:

Students who are looking for home tuition

Teachers who offer paid teaching services

The app allows students and teachers to find, contact, and meet each other for educational purposes.

2. Information We Collect
A. Teacher Information (Required for Security)

To maintain safety, trust, and authenticity on the platform, teachers are required to provide:

Full name

CNIC number

CNIC image

Live photograph (identity verification)

Basic contact and teaching-related information

This information is collected strictly for verification and security purposes.

B. Student Information

Students may provide limited personal information such as:

Name

Contact details

Location (optional, for better matching)

3. How We Use Your Information

Collected information is used only to:

Verify teacher identities

Ensure platform safety and trust

Enable matching between students and teachers

Prevent fraud, impersonation, or misuse

üëâ We do NOT:

Sell personal data

Use data for advertising

Use data for analytics or research

Share data for commercial purposes

4. Data Sharing & Legal Disclosure

Ilmify does not access or use user data under normal circumstances.

User data may be shared only when legally required, including:

Emergency situations

Requests from legal or government authorities

Compliance with applicable laws

This is done solely for user safety and legal compliance.

5. Data Storage & Security

We apply reasonable security measures to protect personal data against:

Unauthorized access

Alteration or misuse

Loss or disclosure

Sensitive identity data is handled carefully and accessed only when absolutely necessary.

6. Camera & Media Access

Ilmify uses camera and media permissions only to:

Capture live verification photos

Upload CNIC images

Upload profile images

These permissions are used only with user consent and for stated purposes.

